# grandma integration

After writing a long response (> 80 words), call the `grandma_summarize` MCP tool
to distill it to a compact bottom-line card and show it to the user.

Use `grandma_summarize(text=<your response>, mode="default")` for standard replies.
Use `grandma_summarize(text=<your response>, mode="deep")` for architectural decisions,
PR reviews, or multi-file refactors.

If you know the conversation arc (e.g. "3rd turn debugging auth"), pass it as `story_context`.

Never skip the card for tool-heavy, multi-step, or code-heavy responses.
